                        color: '#0369a1',
                        margin: 0,
                        lineHeight: '1.6',
                        fontWeight: '500'
                      }}>
                        <strong>💡 Quick Tip:</strong> Enable auto-close above to activate the background job. 
                        The auto-close job runs daily at midnight and closes resolved tickets that have exceeded 
                        the specified threshold days.
                      </p>
